description:
This is a 6 minute workout called 'Instructional: Core Engagement' from the channel Dani Hansen.
The workout falls under Warm-up/Warm-up.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The The Meditative Grind vibe means Zone in, lock down, let repetition take over. This is especially good for Those who love a slow burn and rhythmic intensity. The The Reboot Workout vibe means Deep stretch, low stress, total-body refresh. This is especially good for Recovery days, stress relief, post-travel stiffness..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Ignite your core and feel it with every stroke with Dani in this instructional. ...
